data.description: Darling home in the heart of Little Rock.  This all brick home sits on a larger corner lot and features 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  Kitchen is has white cabinets, glass tile back splash, stainless appliances and a breakfast bar.   Kitchen/dining combo with built in desk area.  Living room has wood floors and large windows with views of front yard.  3 good sized bedrooms. Fully fenced backyard with side entry carport.   Just minutes to interstate access, shopping, food and Boyle Park.
